OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis axes staff bonus
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fand plans to cut jobs      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, John Lewis has axed its staff bonus for
OL,6, a second time and signalled job cuts   
OL,7, are in the pipeline, after what it     
OL,8, described as a "very tough year".      
OL,10,FThe department store firm, which also  
OL,11,Fowns Waitrose supermarkets, reported a 
OL,12,F#234m pre-tax loss.                    
OL,14,FCompany chair Dame Sharon White said   
OL,15,Fthe stores had attracted more          
OL,16,Fcustomers, but they had spent less.    
OL,18,FShe said the losses meant bonuses could
OL,19,Fnot be issued this year for the second 
OL,20,Ftime since it began the scheme in 1953.
